msgctxt "1612"
msgid "Akiyama"
msgstr "Akiyama"

msgctxt "1616"
msgid "Player"
msgstr "Player"

msgctxt "228_Akiyama"
msgid "(That settles that. I should go back to Sky Finance and sit down before I come back.)"
msgstr "(Listo, ya está. Mejor me regreso a Sky Finance y me siento un rato antes de volver)."

msgctxt "240_Akiyama"
msgid "(I should take care of things I might regret not doing. Once that's taken care of, I should go back to Sky Finance and sit down before I come back.)"
msgstr "(Debería ocuparme de las cosas que luego me arrepentiría de no hacer. Una vez resuelto eso, mejor vuelvo a Sky Finance y me siento tranquilo antes de regresar)."

msgctxt "288_Akiyama"
msgid "(The girl we were training at Elise just disappeared.)"
msgstr "(La chica que estaba entrenando en el Elise ha desaparecido)."

msgctxt "300_Akiyama"
msgid "(I need to find her quickly. Where would she be... Maybe where we recruited her?)"
msgstr "(Necesito encontrarla rápido. ¿Dónde podría estar? ¿Tal vez donde la reclute?)."

msgctxt "312_Akiyama"
msgid "(I need to scout some girls for the club right now. If I want to quit scouting, I should head back to Elise.)"
msgstr "(Tengo que buscar chicas para el club ahorita. Si quiero dejar de buscar, mejor me voy de vuelta a Elise)."

msgctxt "336_Player"
msgid "(This is New Serena... There's some scary looking people that come here from time to time and it's members only, so it's hard to go in.)"
msgstr "(Este es el New Serena... A veces viene gente que da miedo y es solo para miembros, así que es difícil entrar)."

msgctxt "348_Player"
msgid "(This is New Serena... Looks like it's members only.)"
msgstr "(Este es el New Serena... Parece que es solo para miembros)."

